Class VariableTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.VariableTracker

  • public class VariableTracker
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores static variables for data sharing between pages. For example when the user logs in their personal details are stored here (exept password). Also when the user selects a combination of movie-day-time, those information are stored here and retrieved from the SeatSelection controller
